    "text": "Got your photo. That's Nate holding a hammer right? Boy looks like he belongs in the maintenance crew at Bethlehem.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-29T09:08:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "48571512477580219",
    "username": "karen"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "65096036785214350",
    "like_count": "21",
    "media_id": "69747148016178032",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000001",
    "text": "Roger sent Karen that photo of Nate at the lake. Reminded me of when Jeff used to fish down by Mina. Good kid.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-29T17:20:06+00:00",
    "user_id": "17944339067641524",
    "username": "roger"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "47559807846368870",
    "like_count": "14",
    "media_id": "14835455871153120",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000002",
    "text": "That Nate's getting big. Looks just like Roger did at that age, swear to God. You see this?",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-27T22:41:57+00:00",
    "user_id": "50100632274746077",
    "username": "jeff"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "19673844477892728",
    "like_count": "13",
    "media_id": "27234814334589625",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000003",
    "text": "Well look at that. You got taller than me somehow. Karen's gonna cry when she sees this.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-29T09:33:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "61374554526679479",
    "username": "nate"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "25262726919256916",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "14307705364695398",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000004",
    "text": "Well. That's a good one. Gonna show Dale at Koffee Kup tomorrow morning.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-29T23:52:07+00:00",
    "user_id": "51622025388870603",
    "username": "emma"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "34263042173764801",
    "like_count": "23",
    "media_id": "77271902743153050",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000005",
    "text": "Well look at that. You're gonna be taller than Jeff before long. Showed Dale this morning, he got a kick out of it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-26T17:25:07+00:00",
    "user_id": "29124510183612267",
    "username": "tyler"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "86054463815157900",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "54575537639471146",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000006",
    "text": "Dale that photo of the fellowship hall came out real nice. Pastor's gonna want that for the bulletin.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T20:19:24+00:00",
    "user_id": "73523778376701833",
    "username": "dale"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "58324079410227860",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "45400961475251342",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000007",
    "text": "That your yard on 3rd? Looks like Nate's old baseball diamond after a good rain. \ud83d\ude04",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-22T06:51:30+00:00",
    "user_id": "74000422318453824",
    "username": "elaine"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "16947686285383142",
    "like_count": "13",
    "media_id": "18041885998583774",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000008",
    "text": "Linda that picture of the Nate and Emma by the nativity looks real good. Hung it up in the fellowship hall.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T00:23:52+00:00",
    "user_id": "20669679693091180",
    "username": "linda"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "83725957223806457",
    "like_count": "25",
    "media_id": "41991603682142346",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000009",
    "text": "Barb that photo of Nate helping me sweep the fellowship hall is something else. Karen's gonna want a copy.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-25T19:28:53+00:00",
    "user_id": "79593117255806993",
    "username": "barb"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "42886062480427534",
    "like_count": "23",
    "media_id": "27579415838305784",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000010",
    "text": "Robert \u2014 Emma got a picture of me after I put up the new sign out front. Karen made me stand next to it. \ud83d\ude04",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-26T20:30:19+00:00",
    "user_id": "91066543424802211",
    "username": "robert"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "93373855934657923",
    "like_count": "0",
    "media_id": "42076285025502783",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000011",
    "text": "Nate sent me a pic of his baseball game up in Aberdeen. Kid's got an arm on him. Thought you'd get a kick out of it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-23T17:10:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "90621917153792142",
    "username": "christine"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "27084661810555164",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "33293368790705295",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000012",
    "text": "Saw that photo you sent, Keith. You look about as happy as I do when Pastor asks me to fix the boiler on a Friday.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-20T09:36:48+00:00",
    "user_id": "12053216661457104",
    "username": "keith"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "91360837631437077",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "72069642536242792",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000013",
    "text": "Got the photo Amy. Frames don't look half bad. Nate says I look like his principal. Not sure what to do with that.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-21T16:25:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "83539032525380930",
    "username": "amy"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "83848961588715891",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "25307423922584703",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_000014",
    "text": "Well that don't look right. No wonder the fellowship hall's been cold every Sunday.",
    "timestamp": "2025-12-18T16:01:49+00:00",
    "user_id": "77663176851724004",
    "username": "klein"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "90735370780927950",
    "like_count": "19",
    "media_id": "32604557769944187",
    "parent_id": "parent_id_900015",
    "text": "Got your photo. That's Nate holding a hammer right? Boy looks like he belongs in the maintenance crew at Bethlehem.",
